  Section 2 Brief

  New teams! We're mixing it up and breaking into more functional groups. Engineering in one room, Product/Design/Content in another. New brief. Each team drafts up to five principles which describe how Coach behaves.
  The constraint: your principles should implicitly answer the four questions from the overview:
1. Should Coach appear on every product/screen?
  2. Should any Coach module be accessible from any other module?
  3. Should every past session be available from every module?
  4. Should the Primary pane always match the active Coach conversation — and if not, when should it match?

We'll then come together, share notes, and attempt a synthesis. Bonus points if you can rank your principles in order of importance!

